Installation Instructions
========================

Prerequisites:
  - Python 3.8 or later
  - pip (Python package installer)

Quick install:

  ./configure
  make
  make install

This installs ytran to /usr/local/bin by default.  To change the prefix:

  ./configure --prefix=$HOME/.local
  make
  make install

To uninstall:

  make uninstall

API Keys:

  ytran expects two API key files:

    ~/.youtubetotranscript_api_key   — transcriptapi.com bearer token
    ~/.anthropic_api_key             — Anthropic API key

  Create these files before running ytran.
